high_descs: Take a right at the door, take a left at the fridge and walk to the counter on the right.
Open the left upper cabinet above the counter, pick up the dark blue plate from inside and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the white stove.
Put the plate inside the microwave, heat it, remove it and close the door.
Turn left and walk to the counter on the right next to the stove.
Put the heated dark blue plate on the counter in the middle.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated plate on a counter.

high_descs: Walk to the door then turn right and walk just past the fridge then turn left and walk to the counter to the right of the dishwasher then turn right.
Look up and open the cabinet door in front of you and grab the blue plate before closing the door.
Turn around and walk to the stove that's in front of you slightly to your left.
Look up and warm the in the microwave then take it back out and close the door.
Take a step to your left to face the counter to the left of the stove.
Put the plate on the counter in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm plate on the counter.

high_descs: Walk up to the door, then turn right and begin walking across the room, hang a left and walk over to the counter, then turn right to face the upper cabinets.
Open the leftmost upper cabinet door in front of you and take out the blue plate then close the cabinet.
Turn right and walk forward, then hang a right and walk over to the oven and look up at the microwave.

Open the microwave and put the blue plate inside then close the door and turn on the microwave, after a couple seconds open the microwave back up and take the now heated plate out, then close the microwave.
Turn left and walk forward, then turn right to face the section of counter to the left of the stove.
Put the heated blue plate on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated blue plate on the counter.
